	.string "REVIVE is fantastic!\p"
	.string "Give it to a fainted Pokémon,\n"
	.string "and the Pokémon will arise.\p"
	.string "But be careful, REVIVE doesn't restore\n"
	.string "the used-up PP of moves.$"

